snippet.title: WHALIEN - Trailer Aug 2021
snippet.description:
WHALIEN is a third person physics adventure set aboard a mechanical whale! Use magnetic powers to interact with anything you can find! Solve tricky environment puzzles and save your whale-hearted friend from nasty squiddies!

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1270680/WHALIEN/

Subscribe to our newsletter to keep up to date: https://forbiddenfolds.com/
